{"tid":2205202,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"AEON九龍灣MegaBox店內衣部員工初步確診","createTime":"2020-09-16T15:42:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-16T17:05:21.000Z","uid":5195,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e61443cef43063c732c8d0022006e715c1b28017","tid":2205202,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T15:42:09.000Z","msg":"AEON永旺 (香港）在Facebook專頁公布，獲悉一名九龍灣店一樓內衣部員工初步確診感染2019冠狀病毒，店方已暫停營業，並於今天及明天進行徹底清潔及消毒，周五（18日）才恢復營業。九龍灣店位於企業廣場5期MegaBox一樓。<br />\n<br />\n公司表示，所有與確診者有密切接觸的員工須在家隔離14天， 並安排進行病毒檢測。 期間會密切跟進有關員工的健康狀況，亦會與衛生防護中心緊密聯繫以跟進有關事件。"},{"pid":"2260c7f5487a7434d6111d9fef40ade6fc081dda","tid":2205202,"uid":278507,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T16:19:05.000Z","msg":"Aeon係咪應該要取超三，太危險了"},{"pid":"792c0d26a6658683d977bf74d4cad453e2e9fa81","tid":2205202,"uid":3464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T16:23:26.000Z","msg":"平日超市多人到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依啲黎消毒佢確定有用？<br />\n做佢員工真係慘"},{"pid":"16a7fb8ca929403800b21054c25302cc2bee1a20","tid":2205202,"uid":278507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T16:38:42.000Z","msg":"真的有全店消毒及深層消潔嗎？"},{"pid":"b11c571eaea0d5c88b70bde99b67a8942f8f4487","tid":2205202,"uid":193476,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2260c7f5487a7434d6111d9fef40ade6fc081dda","tid":2205202,"uid":278507,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T16:19:05.000Z","msg":"Aeon係咪應該要取超三，太危險了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T16:47:36.000Z","msg":"雖然你無講錯，但係日日返工放工巴士地鐵迫滿晒人咪又一樣危險"},{"pid":"f9c61ef187f2cc63ac74e71557c5e7dadffefcc5","tid":2205202,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"792c0d26a6658683d977bf74d4cad453e2e9fa81","tid":2205202,"uid":3464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T16:23:26.000Z","msg":"平日超市多人到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依啲黎消毒佢確定有用？<br />\n做佢員工真係慘"}